00:25:28,440 --> 00:25:30,440
Is this an episode?
Is this one of Will's episodes?

315
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:32,610
No. No! No. <font color="#ff00ff">[scoffs]</font>

316
00:25:32,690 --> 00:25:35,570
<font color="#ff00ff">[stutters]</font> I'm sorry. I just... I don't...

