00:26:26,830 --> 00:26:29,750
And that's the giveaway.
That's the giveaway. Ha!

337
00:26:29,830 --> 00:26:31,270
Don't you get it? It's not a puzzle,

338
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:33,090
it's a map.

