00:26:47,810 --> 00:26:48,980
<font color="#ff00ff">[radio static]</font>

344
00:26:49,060 --> 00:26:50,310
<font color="#ff00ff">[Hopper]</font> Does anybody copy?

345
00:26:51,150 --> 00:26:54,770
Look, if anybody copies,
