00:28:41,210 --> 00:28:42,300
<font color="#ff00ff">[stutters]</font> Is he with Mike?

366
00:28:42,380 --> 00:28:45,970
Like I said,
I don't know and I don't care.

367
00:28:46,050 --> 00:28:49,850
Please tell him it's super important.
Please tell him that I have a code...

